DICOM dictionary¶

DicomDictionary¶

class imebra::DicomDictionary¶

Provides information about the tag’s description and their default data type (VR).

tagId_t¶

enum imebra::tagId_t¶

Enumerates the tags stored in the DicomDictionary.

Can be used with TagId to create an ID for a known tag.

Unlike other enumerations, each item starts with an uppercase letter, to reflect the tag name used in the Dicom standard.

Warning
Very large enumeration classes cause an error in Java, therefore the tagId_t enumeration is not supported in Java.
